(* other static configurations *)
staticZCenterVectors={{0,0,1}};

staticZXCenterVectors={{0,0,1},{1,0,0}};

staticZYCenterVectors={{0,0,1},{0,1,0}};

staticZMZCenterVectors={{0,0,1},{0,0,-1}};
(* compute  Subscript[w, l] expansion coeffs *)
w0tilde[\[Alpha]d_]:=w0tilde[\[Alpha]d]=Sqrt[\[Pi]]*(1-Cos[\[Alpha]d]);

wltilde[l_,\[Alpha]d_]:=wltilde[l,\[Alpha]d]=Sqrt[\[Pi]*(2*l+1)]/l*(Cos[\[Alpha]d]*LegendreP[l,Cos[\[Alpha]d]]-LegendreP[l+1,Cos[\[Alpha]d]]);

clsq[l_,\[Alpha]d_,\[Beta]JK_]:=clsq[l,\[Alpha]d,\[Beta]JK]=wltilde[l,\[Alpha]d]^2*LegendreP[l,Cos[\[Beta]JK]];

getSymmetricClMatrix[l_,\[Alpha]d_,domainCenters_]:=Module[{tmp1},(
tmp1=Table[Chop[clsq[l,\[Alpha]d,VectorAngle[domainCenters[[J]],domainCenters[[K]]]]],{K,Length[domainCenters]},{J,1,K}];
Return[MapThread[Join,{tmp1,Rest/@Flatten[tmp1,{{2},{1}}]}]]
)];

(* calculates the unscaled form factor coefficients Subscript[C, l]. strTerms can take the values "total", "intra", or "inter" *)
getcl[domainCenters_,ad_,maxL_]:=Module[{Nd,\[Alpha]d,clMatrixList,cl},(
Nd=Length[domainCenters];
\[Alpha]d=get\[Alpha]N[ad,Nd];
clMatrixList=ParallelTable[getSymmetricClMatrix[l,\[Alpha]d,domainCenters],{l,maxL}];
(* the overall coefficient list vector (length maxL) is the total of all matrix elements *)
cl=Chop[Map[Total[Flatten[#]]&,clMatrixList]];
Return[cl]
)];

(* returns the domain half-angle for N monodisperse domains with total area fraction ad *)
get\[Alpha]N[ad_,N_]:=ArcCos[1-2*ad/N];
(* compute wtildeL: example  *)
(* Clear[ad];
{Nd,maxL}={12,40};
domainCenters=getDomainCenterVectorsPredefined["platonic",Nd];
{time,wl}=AbsoluteTiming[getcl[domainCenters,ad,maxL]];
time
wl/.ad\[Rule]0.25 *)
